extendedInfo.description: If you are Panic! At The Disco's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Panic! At The Disco's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Panic! At The Disco's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Panic! At The Disco's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)--------------------------------Main Features --------------------------------- Lyrics categorized by album - Show all lyrics - Search lyrics--------------------------------List of albums --------------------------------- A Fever You Can't Sweat Out- Pretty. Odd.- Vices & Virtues--------------------------------List of lyrics --------------------------------- Always- Behind The Sea- Behind The Sea (Alternate Version)- Bittersweet- Build God, Then We'll Talk- But It's Better If You Do- Camisado- Do You Know What I'm Seeing?- Do You Know What I'm Seeing? reviews.title: 5 star deserving, but...
reviews.comment: I love P!atD. This app is a good one, but the newest album, \'Too weird to live, Too rare to die\' needs to be added for a five star rating.
reviews.author: Tavros NoMoreBuckets Nitram

reviews.title: Not all the songs are here!
reviews.comment: I really love this app but it\'s missing some songs (especially the new song). I love using this app but it really annoys me when I don\'t see some songs I want to see, like New Perspective. It would be great if we can get those songs and probably the new one.
